data.description: Spacious 3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom Home in Robinson, Texas?Looking for a charming home in Robinson, Texas? Look no further! This roomy home has everything you need, from two living areas to a double lot that leaves plenty of room for your imagination. The home is a grand 1,531 square feet, providing ample space for your next gathering. You'll also be pleased to know that the property is conveniently located only 0.3 miles away from Alta Vista Elementary and 0.4 miles away from University High School. The security system and solar panels are included with the home and have already been paid for. Don't miss out – schedule a viewing today!
